title: V (Original Series) - Complete Collection (1983-1985) DVD Remux
description:
V (Original Series) - The Complete Collection (1983-1985)

These are straight up remux's of the dvd's with MakeMKV
These where super hard to get

Mini Series and Final Battle i managed to source the us dvd9's
Complete series i couldnt find the us dvd9's so had to source the pal dvd9's

Luckily none of the disc's where interlaced and are 23.976 fps with software flags for 30fps
so no hard telecine..
